{"3633770": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "LAT 觸手怪物的龐克世界", "steam_appid": 3633770, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲概要</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《LAT 觸手怪物的龐克世界》是一款重口味的觸手題材RPG遊戲。玩家將扮演底層觸手居民（觸手君），邂逅各式各樣的女性，展開一段奇幻又溫馨的觸手人生～</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras/ed71d84357002138bfa46d8ae61ff5ef.poster.avif?t=1776157655\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras/ed71d84357002138bfa46d8ae61ff5ef.webm?t=1776157655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras/ed71d84357002138bfa46d8ae61ff5ef.mp4?t=1776157655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲劇情</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是一個光怪陸離的人類與觸手怪物共存的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你，身為底層觸手居民，生活在一個人類至上的國家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某天，你意外覺醒了稀有能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為了獲得更好的生存環境，也為了報答多次拯救過你的觸手（大師），你順水推舟的選擇加入觸手自救組織。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >憑藉著稀有的能力，你迅速成為組織骨幹，並在不知不覺間推動了歷史進程的齒輪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如今，你已身處風暴的中心，但你的初衷……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras/f93b88050abb77e7c1596c80a8f5134d.poster.avif?t=1776157655\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras/f93b88050abb77e7c1596c80a8f5134d.webm?t=1776157655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras/f93b88050abb77e7c1596c80a8f5134d.mp4?t=1776157655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要人物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35 歲的高齡妓女</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搶劫受賄的女警察</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邪教組織的女主教</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觸手天敵的女特工</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras/3f455408e32aad350d9479179e9f9eee.avif?t=1776157655\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras_big/3f455408e32aad350d9479179e9f9eee.avif?t=1776157655 width=800 height=566 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CG</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >動態性愛場景，CG數量300+（含差分）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras/3553aff314b8f8c947dfa8bce68e0301.poster.avif?t=1776157655\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras/3553aff314b8f8c947dfa8bce68e0301.webm?t=1776157655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras/3553aff314b8f8c947dfa8bce68e0301.mp4?t=1776157655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>稀有能力</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用這稀有的能力，一點一點探索女性的內心世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讓女性＂心甘情願＂成為你的孕袋和母豬吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633770/extras/8be049cc41a8be0e75ccad97aa2a8e17.poster.avif?t=1776157655\" w